metadata.name: A Tale of a rabbit sleepwalking#001
metadata.description: A loner rabbit, tired of living the same life every day with the rest of his pack. One day, it and the rabbits in the river to drink water, accidentally saw the water under their own, it was surprised to find that it had a hand in the water to greet themselves. So it nods politely in response, only to be sucked into another world underwater. It begins a magical journey...
